longBusinessSummary: home24 SE, together with its subsidiaries, markets, sells, and ships furniture and home furnishings in Europe and Brazil. It offers living, dining, and bedroom, upholstered, and garden furniture; mattresses; lighting products; and lamps and accessories. The company sells its products under the Studio Copenhagen, ARS NATURA, MORTEENS, ars MANUFACTI, Masion Belfort, fredriks, home24, and Mobly brand names. It operates 18 showrooms in Germany, Austria, Switzerland, and Brazil, as well as nine outlets in Germany and Brazil; and an online platform. home24 SE was incorporated in 2009 and is headquartered in Berlin, Germany.
